==Documentation==
This template creates the individual game cards that show on the Games and home pages. The data is passed into this template from Module:GameQuery

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Title || The original game name / path in wiki
|-
|| CleanTitle || The name with Games/ removed
|-
|| Platforms || List of platforms
|-
|| Date || Date in YYYY Month DD format
|-
|| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|-
|| Image || Thumbnail image in raw format
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
Called from Module:GameQuery not directly used.
</pre>
</noinclude>
<div class="listing-card">
    <div class="listing-card-link clickable-box" data-url="{{fullurl:{{{url_title}}}}}">
        <div class="listing-card-image gb-game-hero-cover">
            {{#if: {{{image|}}} | 
                {{{image}}}
                | 
                <div class="no-image">No Image Available</div> 
            }}
        </div>
        <div class="listing-card-info">
            <h3 class="listing-card-title">{{{title}}}</h3>
            <div class="listing-card-meta">{{{release_date|Unknown Release}}}</div>
            <div class="listing-card-deck">{{{deck|}}}</div>
            <div class="platform-badges">
                {{#invoke:BadgeList|format|{{{platforms|}}}}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
